<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: The Quest for Exotic Ingredients (help needed)</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Xarn">Xarn</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 12:03 p.m. 16/8/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: The Quest for Exotic Ingredients (help needed)<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/quest.cgi?read=525" TARGET=_self>The Quest for Exotic Ingredients (help needed)</A> (Korbac)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> So one day I was visiting my favorite shady tavern in Freeport,

<BR>&gt; when the bartender there told me of a beverage he wished to make
<BR>&gt; if I could bring him the following four ingredients:
<P>&gt; Kiola Nut, which is found on the various ocean islands.
<P>&gt; Honey Jum, made by a shopkeeper in Rivervale.
<P>&gt; Koalindl Fish, found only in the pool of the Temple of Life in
<BR>&gt; Qeynos.
<P>&gt; Erud's Tonic, made in Erudin, but illegal to smuggle from the
<BR>&gt; city.
<P>&gt; So far I have managed to procure the Kiola Nut and the Honey
<BR>&gt; Jum, but I'll be damned if I can figure out how to get a
<BR>&gt; Koalindl Fish (I have not attempted to get the Erud's Tonic
<BR>&gt; yet). Does ANYONE have any idea how I'm supposed to get a
<BR>&gt; Koalindl? There seems to be a side quest - a dog named Frostbite
<BR>&gt; occasionally steals one of the fish from the pool, and the Guard
<BR>&gt; there asks you to recover it for him. I've tried killing the dog
<BR>&gt; (which seriously ticked off the owners), and I've tried talking
<BR>&gt; to the owners, but still can't figure it out.
<P>&gt; Anybody have an idea? Oh, and fishing in the pool only gets you
<BR>&gt; normal fish.
<P>&gt; Thanks in advance for any help, and if you happen to be on
<BR>&gt; Bristlebane, I'll pay you 2 platinum if you either bring me the
<BR>&gt; fish or help me to get it.
<P>&gt; Korbac
<BR>&gt; Half Elf Scout of Tunare
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
